These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
City: miami, prague, nizza
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
3. the person traveling to miami is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to prague is the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| City    | prague    | nizza | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, chef, police-officer
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the accountant is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the police-officer##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Job       | chef | police-officer | accountant |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, musical, crime
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre         | crime     | musical | romance |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, doctor, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the doctor is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the coach is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the doctor is in an even position##4
4. the doctor is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Job   | police-officer | doctor  | coach  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, volleyball, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Sport   | volleyball | parkour     | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, light-blue, lavender
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who likes blue is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Color   | light-blue | lavender | blue   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

