2. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Flower    | balloon-flower    | marigold | poppy     |

