.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia, rose
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Flower   | rose   | begonia  | sunflower  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

