.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, skydiving, writing
There 3 different types of food: corn, garlic, pineapple
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing    | writing      | skydiving |
| Food       | garlic | pineapple | corn   |

