2. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

