.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the australian is the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| Sport     | baseball     | cricket   | soccer        |

