.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the french##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the dutch##1
3. the french is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | french  | canadian | dutch   |
| Beverage         | lemonade | soy-milk   | fanta |

