.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, sprite
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking 7up and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up | sprite | water |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

