.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, victorian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the victorian house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
4. the victorian house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| House   | gothic-revival  | victorian     | farmhouse |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

