.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, thai, turkish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, july, february
1. the american is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
4. the thai is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | american | turkish | thai    |
| Birthday           | july     | february  | april |

