.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, bike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the bike is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Transport         | bike | jet-ski   | quad-bike |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | classical | jazz      |

