.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, turtle
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, lily
1. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | hamster  | turtle   | guinea-pig |
| Flower   | lily | sunflower | begonia       |

 